msgstr "基于 link:https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java[grpc-java] 的 link:https://grpc.github.io/grpc/core/md_doc_grpc_xds_features.html[xDS gRPC] 封装层，配有独立的基于 Netty 的 gRPC 服务器"

#: _versions/3.6/guides/grpc-getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Further docs explain how to enable and use each of them."
