#: _versions/3.6/guides/grpc-getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Extends the `ImplBase` class. This is a generated class."
msgstr "继承自 `ImplBase` 类。这是一个生成的类。"

#: _versions/3.6/guides/grpc-getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
